{"type": "article", "id": 11341, "title": "保时捷 911 Targa 复古跑车改装版", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-29T11:12:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607184147T2BaUPE9xSJ7k31j.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自美国加州的知名汽车改装工作室 Singer Vehicle Design 擅长改装各式复古跑车，最近他们又带来一款改装新作，是基于经典跑车保时捷 911 Targa 的再设计。动力方面，Singer Vehicle Design 为这台车搭载了一个动力强劲的 4.0 升六缸发动机，可以提供 390hp 的动力输出和 315lb-ft 的峰值扭矩，让这台古董级跑车重新焕发出新的活力。而在外观方面，设计团队也为其换上了亮灰色的涂装。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607184144QzZ960Ew7OHxfFmp.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607184144eRJK5d3lxwvLi74a.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071841459X6wUOTj27D3WnuB.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607184145SYUF9qLKEWpNcTti.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607184146GRHcdroMZ640zvVX.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}